STATE
v.
FISHER 2019-0158 Supreme Court of Ohio. March 20, 2019

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

On review of an order certifying a conflict. The court determines that a conflict exists. Sua sponte, cause held for the decision in 2018-0012, State v. Hitchcock, and briefing schedule stayed. DEWINE, J., dissents.
